trans-unit.source: The exception that is thrown when the workflow runtime engine attempts to load a workflow instance that is currently loaded by another workflow runtime engine instance.
trans-unit.target: 워크플로 런타임 엔진이 현재 다른 워크플로 런타임 엔진 인스턴스에 의해 로드된 워크플로 인스턴스를 로드하려고 하면 예외가 throw됩니다.

trans-unit.source: Additionally, this exception is thrown when the workflow runtime engine attempts to save a workflow after the ownership timeout that was specified while loading the workflow has expired.
trans-unit.target: 또한 워크플로를 로드하는 동안 지정된 소유권 시간 제한이 만료된 후 워크플로 런타임 엔진이 워크플로를 저장하려고 하면 이 예외가 throw됩니다.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowOwnershipException> is used by persistence services which support the capability for multiple applications to access the same database.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowOwnershipException>은 여러 응용 프로그램이 동일한 데이터베이스에 액세스하는 기능을 지원하는 지속성 서비스에서 사용됩니다.

trans-unit.source: In such an environment, an instance of the workflow runtime may try to load a workflow that is already loaded by another instance of the workflow runtime engine.
trans-unit.target: 이러한 환경에서 워크플로 런타임 인스턴스는 워크플로 런타임 엔진의 다른 인스턴스에 의해 이미 로드된 워크플로를 로드하려고 할 수 있습니다.

trans-unit.source: For example, the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Hosting.SqlWorkflowPersistenceService> class throws the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowOwnershipException> when this situation occurs.
trans-unit.target: 예를 들어 <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Hosting.SqlWorkflowPersistenceService> 클래스는 이 경우가 발생할 때 <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowOwnershipException>을 throw합니다.

trans-unit.source: If you implement a persistence service that throws the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowOwnershipException> you should provide the <xref:System.Guid> of the workflow instance for which the exception occurs by using an appropriate constructor for the class or setting the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowOwnershipException.InstanceId%2A> property before you throw the exception.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowOwnershipException>을 throw하는 지속성 서비스를 구현하는 경우 예외를 throw하기 전에 클래스에 적절한 생성자를 사용하거나 <xref:System.Guid> 속성을 설정하여 예외가 발생하는 워크플로 인스턴스의 <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowOwnershipException.InstanceId%2A>를 제공해야 합니다.

trans-unit.source: Sets the <see cref="T:System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo" /> object with the <see cref="T:System.Guid" /> of the workflow instance associated with this exception, and additional exception information.
trans-unit.target: 이 예외와 연결된 워크플로 인스턴스의 <see cref="T:System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo" /> 및 추가 예외 정보를 사용하여 <see cref="T:System.Guid" /> 개체를 설정합니다.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowOwnershipException.GetObjectData%2A> sets a <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo> with all the exception object data targeted for serialization.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowOwnershipException.GetObjectData%2A>는 serialization을 위해 대상으로 하는 모든 예외 개체 데이터를 사용하여 <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo>를 설정합니다.

trans-unit.source: During deserialization the exception object is reconstituted from the <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo> transmitted over the stream.
trans-unit.target: deserialization을 수행하는 동안 스트림을 통해 전송된 <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo>에서 예외 개체가 다시 구성됩니다.

trans-unit.source: For more information see XML and SOAP Serialization.
trans-unit.target: 자세한 내용은 XML 및 SOAP Serialization을 참조하십시오.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="info" /> is a null reference (<see langword="Nothing" /> in Visual Basic)
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="info" />이 null 참조(Visual Basic의 경우 <see langword="Nothing" />)인 경우

trans-unit.source: Gets the <see cref="T:System.Guid" /> of the workflow instance for which this exception was thrown.
trans-unit.target: 이 예외가 throw된 워크플로 인스턴스의 <see cref="T:System.Guid" />를 가져옵니다.

trans-unit.source: <see cref="P:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowOwnershipException.InstanceId" /> is equivalent to the <see cref="P:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowInstance.InstanceId" /> property of the workflow instance.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="P:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowOwnershipException.InstanceId" />는 워크플로 인스턴스의 <see cref="P:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowInstance.InstanceId" /> 속성과 같습니다.
